Strathon is a multi-component project with components under different
open-source licenses. The summary:

  sdk/        Apache License 2.0   (see sdk/LICENSE)
  receiver/   MIT License          (see receiver/LICENSE)
  examples/   MIT License          (same terms as receiver)
  docs/       MIT License
  tests/      MIT License

See LICENSING.md for the rationale behind the split.

When in doubt about a specific file, the license that applies is the one
of the LICENSE file in the nearest enclosing directory; if none, the
component's LICENSE applies; if neither, the MIT terms in receiver/LICENSE
apply.

